```mermaid
classDiagram
direction TB

class "Presentation Layer\n(API / Services)" as PL {
  +API Endpoints / Controllers
  +Application Services
}

class "Business Logic Layer\n(Core Models)" as BL {
  +HBnBFacade <<Facade>>
  +User
  +Place
  +Review
  +Amenity
  +Business Rules / Validation
}

class "Persistence Layer\n(Data Access)" as DAL {
  +Repositories / DAOs
  +Database
}

PL --> BL : calls Facade
BL --> DAL : data operations
